    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next adventure? This beauty has been so good to me and is still running like a champ! It\u2019s in great shape overall\u2014just a few tiny signs of love from the road, but honestly, it looks and drives fantastic. Perfect for someone who wants a solid, dependable car without the brand-new price tag. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 33500.0,
