    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo, featuring the iconic 2JZ-GTE inline-six power plant and factory sequential twin-turbochargers. Power is delivered through the bulletproof Getrag V160 six-speed manual transmission to a Torsen limited-slip differential. The vehicle maintains its original double-wishbone suspension geometry, providing exceptional lateral stability and feedback. This example shows consistent boost pressure across the RPM range with no evidence of shaft play in the snails or synchro grind in the higher gears. While the chassis shows minor cosmetic patina, the mechanical vitals\u2014including cooling system integrity and compression across all six cylinders\u2014are robust. A purist\u2019s spec, free of aftermarket ECU interference, retaining the original longitudinal balance and torsional rigidity that defined the A80 generation.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Used vehicle in good condition. Mechanically sound. Clean title. Regular maintenance history. Minor cosmetic wear only.",
      "price": 36500.0,
