      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, making it perfect for someone looking for a reliable daily driver without the 'new car' price tag. It runs like a dream and is ready for its next adventure with you. Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 31500.0,
