    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically robust 2008 Porsche 911 Carrera (997.1). This example features the 3.6L M97 flat-six engine, known for its visceral power delivery and integrated dry-sump lubrication. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission offers precise shift gates with no synchro grind. The hydraulic steering rack provides the communicative feedback lost in later electric systems. Recent preventative maintenance includes an Air-Oil Separator (AOS) replacement and a clutch service. The chassis remains taut, utilizing its original multi-link rear suspension geometry for optimal corner-exit traction. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with a well-loved driver, the four-piston monoblock calipers and ventilated rotors ensure peak deceleration performance.",
